Parse Multiple Classroom Codes

Source: R/utils-classroom-code.R
parse_classroom_codes.Rd

Vectorized version of parse_classroom_code(). Parses a vector of classroom codes and returns a tibble with parsed components plus the delivery type name.

Usage

parse_classroom_codes(codes)

Arguments

codes

Character vector of classroom codes.

Value

A tibble with columns: county_code, delivery_type_code, delivery_type, program_code, class_num.

Examples

parse_classroom_codes(c("823P012601.01", "456C789.02"))
#> # A tibble: 2 × 5
#>   county_code delivery_type_code program_code class_num delivery_type     
#>   <chr>       <chr>              <chr>        <chr>     <chr>             
#> 1 823         P                  012601       01        Public School     
#> 2 456         C                  789          02        Private Child Care
